s:47:\"Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 open for registration\";s:3:\"log\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"comment\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"promote\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"sticky\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"nid\";s:2:\"12\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"article\";s:8:\"language\";s:3:\"und\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1300882273\";s:7:\"changed\";s:10:\"1348559124\";s:4:\"tnid\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"translate\";s:1:\"0\";s:18:\"revision_timestamp\";s:10:\"1348559124\";s:12:\"revision_uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:3104:\"<p>We announce that Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 is&nbsp;<strong>open for registration</strong>on the event website at&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">b2011.drupalcamp.ro</a>.</p>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;currently organizes its second major event:<a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011</a>, taking place during 7th and 8th of May, 2011 after the successful&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://tm2010.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://tm2010.drupalcamp.ro/\">first Romanian Drupalcamp</a>&nbsp;organized in Timisoara - last year.</p>\r\n<p>The event is organized in partnership with&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.ccs.ro\" href=\"http://www.ccs.ro/\">Student&#39;s Culture House of Bucharest</a>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.mcsi.ro\" href=\"http://www.mcsi.ro/\">Romanian Ministry of Communication and Information Society</a>. There are sponsors and media partners that have already joined the event:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<a>Gold Sponsors:&nbsp;</a><a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.epayment.ro/\" href=\"http://www.epayment.ro/\">GECAD ePayment</a></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Community Sponsors:&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://corporate.adulmec.ro/\" href=\"http://corporate.adulmec.ro/\">Adulmec</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.zitec.com\" href=\"http://www.zitec.com/\">Zitec</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://webikon.com\" href=\"http://webikon.com/\">Webikon</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.hangarhosting.net\" href=\"http://www.hangarhosting.net/\">Hangar Hosting</a></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Media Partners:&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.agora.ro/\" href=\"http://www.agora.ro/\">Agora Group</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.worldit.info/\" href=\"http://www.worldit.info/\">WorldIT</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://osn.ro/\" href=\"http://osn.ro/\">Open Software Network</a>,<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.phpromania.net/\" href=\"http://www.phpromania.net/\">PHPRomania</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.joobs.ro/\" href=\"http://www.joobs.ro/\">Joobs</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://ittrends.ro/\" href=\"http://ittrends.ro/\">IT Trends</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.tehnopol.ro/\" href=\"http://www.tehnopol.ro/\">TehnoPOL</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Registration is opened at&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">b2011.drupalcamp.ro</a>. Stay updated by following our Twitter account&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.twitter.com/drupalromania\" href=\"http://www.twitter.com/drupalromania\">@drupalromania</a>, hashtag&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://twitter.com/#search?q=%23dbuc\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#search?q=%23dbuc\">#dbuc</a>&nbsp;or our<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=111236985619951\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=111236985619951\">event Facebook page</a>. See also our&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/faq\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/faq\">FAQ page</a>&nbsp;for details on registration.</p>\r\n<p>Looking forward to see you in May in Bucharest!</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:2982:\"<p>We announce that Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 is <strong>open for registration</strong>on the event website at <a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">b2011.drupalcamp.ro</a>.</p>\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> currently organizes its second major event:<a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011</a>, taking place during 7th and 8th of May, 2011 after the successful <a fcksavedurl=\"http://tm2010.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://tm2010.drupalcamp.ro/\">first Romanian Drupalcamp</a> organized in Timisoara - last year.</p>\n<p>The event is organized in partnership with <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.ccs.ro\" href=\"http://www.ccs.ro/\">Student\'s Culture House of Bucharest</a> and the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.mcsi.ro\" href=\"http://www.mcsi.ro/\">Romanian Ministry of Communication and Information Society</a>. There are sponsors and media partners that have already joined the event:</p>\n<ul><li>\n		<a>Gold Sponsors: </a><a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.epayment.ro/\" href=\"http://www.epayment.ro/\">GECAD ePayment</a></li>\n<li>\n		Community Sponsors: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://corporate.adulmec.ro/\" href=\"http://corporate.adulmec.ro/\">Adulmec</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.zitec.com\" href=\"http://www.zitec.com/\">Zitec</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://webikon.com\" href=\"http://webikon.com/\">Webikon</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.hangarhosting.net\" href=\"http://www.hangarhosting.net/\">Hangar Hosting</a></li>\n<li>\n		Media Partners: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.agora.ro/\" href=\"http://www.agora.ro/\">Agora Group</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.worldit.info/\" href=\"http://www.worldit.info/\">WorldIT</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://osn.ro/\" href=\"http://osn.ro/\">Open Software Network</a>,<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.phpromania.net/\" href=\"http://www.phpromania.net/\">PHPRomania</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.joobs.ro/\" href=\"http://www.joobs.ro/\">Joobs</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://ittrends.ro/\" href=\"http://ittrends.ro/\">IT Trends</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.tehnopol.ro/\" href=\"http://www.tehnopol.ro/\">TehnoPOL</a></li>\n</ul><p>Registration is opened at <a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/\">b2011.drupalcamp.ro</a>. Stay updated by following our Twitter account <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.twitter.com/drupalromania\" href=\"http://www.twitter.com/drupalromania\">@drupalromania</a>, hashtag <a fcksavedurl=\"http://twitter.com/#search?q=%23dbuc\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#search?q=%23dbuc\">#dbuc</a> or our<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=111236985619951\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=111236985619951\">event Facebook page</a>. See also our <a fcksavedurl=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/faq\" href=\"http://b2011.drupalcamp.ro/faq\">FAQ page</a> for details on registration.</p>\n<p>Looking forward to see you in May in Bucharest!</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:10:\"field_tags\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:2:{i:0;a:1:{s:3:\"tid\";s:1:\"9\";}i:1;a:1:{s:3:\"tid\";s:1:\"1\";}}}s:16:\"field_main_image\";a:0:{}s:12:\"field_images\";a:0:{}s:11:\"title_field\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"value\";s:47:\"Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 open for registration\";s:6:\"format\";N;s:10:\"safe_value\";s:47:\"Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 open for registration\";}}}s:22:\"field_main_image_style\";a:0:{}s:14:\"title_original\";s:47:\"Drupalcamp Bucharest 2011 open for registration\";s:12:\"translations\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"original\";s:3:\"und\";s:4:\"data\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:9:{s:11:\"entity_type\";s:4:\"node\";s:9:\"entity_id\";s:2:\"12\";s:8:\"language\";s:3:\"und\";s:6:\"source\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"translate\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1348555785\";s:7:\"changed\";s:10:\"1348555785\";}}}s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:11:{s:11:\"field_image\";a:2:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:2:{i:0;s:8:\"og:image\";i:1;s:12:\"rdfs:seeAlso\";}s:4:\"type\";s:3:\"rel\";}s:10:\"field_tags\";a:2