announce the creation of&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>. The main goal of the association is to promote Drupal CMS as an opersource system for the development of web portals and applications.</p>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;is a non-profit and apolitical Romanian legal entity. The Association&rsquo;s founding members are&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>,<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The recently established Romanian association aims to promote&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>, to help the Romanian Drupal community by providing support and translated documentation, to organize events (conferences, workshops, meetings, presentations, open trainings, media events). Various companies, public institutions and NGOs will be contacted as partners for the promotion of&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;is a contributor as well as a participant to the global&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;Community.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"FCK__PageBreak\" drupalbreak=\"true\" fckfakelement=\"true\" fckrealelement=\"1\" src=\"http://drupal.org.ro/sites/all/modules/fckeditor/fckeditor/editor/images/spacer.gif\" /></p>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;currently organizes its first major event, the Timisoara 2010&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp</a>, taking place during 5<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;and 6<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;of June, 2010. The event is organized in partnership with the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technical University of Timişoara</a>&nbsp;and will host hundreds of users and developers from Romania, Hungary, Ucraine, Serbia, Bosnia, Croatia and other Central and East European states, as well as speakers from the global<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;Community.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Drupal</strong>. It&#39;s a free software package that allows a person or a community to easily publish, manage and organize rich online content. Hundreds of thousands of people and organizations&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">use Drupal</a>&nbsp;to implement various websites, including community portals, discussion groups, intranet applications, personal websites and blogs, e-Commerce applications, repositories and social networks.&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;is<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource software</a>&nbsp;distributed under&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a>&nbsp;(GNU General Public License) and it is maintained and developed by a large community of users and developers.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Drupal Romania Association</strong>. It&#39;s a non-profit and apolitical Romanian legal entity committed to support the development of&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>open source project. The association supports the Romanian community by providing funding, infrastructure, supporting event organization, promoting and distributing Drupal</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Drupalcamp</strong>. It&#39;s an event aimed to leverage the sharing of knowledge about&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;and to facilitate learning&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;in an open environment. Drupalcamp is an intense, participant-driven event, hosting workshops and demos, and following the format of &ldquo;unconferences&rdquo; as opposite to official conferences (such as OSCON, DrupalCon, LinuxCon, etc.). Participants submit proposals before the event is held, and the schedule is designed based on these proposals. The overall goals of Drupalcamp are to connect local and regional communities and to allow the sharing of knowledge.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:4708:\"<p>The Romanian community of <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> users, developers and enthusiasts, announce the creation of <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>. The main goal of the association is to promote Drupal CMS as an opersource system for the development of web portals and applications.</p>\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> is a non-profit and apolitical Romanian legal entity. The Association’s founding members are <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>,<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a> and <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\n<p>The recently established Romanian association aims to promote <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>, to help the Romanian Drupal community by providing support and translated documentation, to organize events (conferences, workshops, meetings, presentations, open trainings, media events). Various companies, public institutions and NGOs will be contacted as partners for the promotion of <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> is a contributor as well as a participant to the global <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> Community.</p>\n\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> currently organizes its first major event, the Timisoara 2010 <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp</a>, taking place during 5th and 6th of June, 2010. The event is organized in partnership with the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technical University of Timişoara</a> and will host hundreds of users and developers from Romania, Hungary, Ucraine, Serbia, Bosnia, Croatia and other Central and East European states, as well as speakers from the global<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> Community.</p>\n<p><strong>About Drupal</strong>. It\'s a free software package that allows a person or a community to easily publish, manage and organize rich online content. Hundreds of thousands of people and organizations <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">use Drupal</a> to implement various websites, including community portals, discussion groups, intranet applications, personal websites and blogs, e-Commerce applications, repositories and social networks. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> is<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource software</a> distributed under <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a> (GNU General Public License) and it is maintained and developed by a large community of users and developers.</p>\n<p><strong>About Drupal Romania Association</strong>. It\'s a non-profit and apolitical Romanian legal entity committed to support the development of <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>open source project. The association supports the Romanian community by providing funding, infrastructure, supporting event organization, promoting and distributing Drupal</p>\n<p><strong>About Drupalcamp</strong>. It\'s an event aimed to leverage the sharing of knowledge about <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> and to facilitate learning <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> in an open environment. Drupalcamp is an intense, participant-driven event, hosting workshops and demos, and following the format of “unconferences” as opposite to official conferences (such as OSCON, DrupalCon, LinuxCon, etc.). Participants submit proposals before the event is held, and the schedule is designed based on these proposals. The overall goals of Drupalcamp are to connect local and regional communities and to allow the sharing of knowledge.</p>\n<p> </p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"ro\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:5581:\"<p>Comunitatea utilizatorilor, dezvoltatorilor şi pasionaţilor de&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;din Rom&acirc;nia anunţă &icirc;nfiinţarea&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţiei Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</a>. Principalul scop al Asociaţiei este promovarea sistemului&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource</a>&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;ca sistem deschis pentru realizarea de situri portaluri web.</p>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</a>&nbsp;este persoană juridică rom&acirc;nă cu caracter non-profit şi apolitică. Membrii fondatori ai Asociaţiei sunt:&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a>&nbsp;şi&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Organizaţia nou &icirc;nfiinţată &icirc;n Rom&acirc;nia &icirc;şi propune promovarea&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>; susţinerea Comunităţii Drupal din Rom&acirc;nia prin furnizarea de suport şi documentaţie localizate &icirc;n rom&acirc;nă; organizarea de evenimente (conferinţe, seminarii, &icirc;nt&acirc;lniri, prezentări, cursuri deschise, evenimente media). Se vor stabili contacte şi parteneriate cu companii, instituţii publice, alte ONG-uri &icirc;n vederea promovării&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</a>&nbsp;este parte şi contribuie la eforturile comunităţii globale<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"FCK__PageBreak\" drupalbreak=\"true\" fckfakelement=\"true\" fckrealelement=\"1\" src=\"http://drupal.org.ro/sites/all/modules/fckeditor/fckeditor/editor/images/spacer.gif\" /></p>\r\n<p>Primul eveniment de marcă al&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţiei Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</a>&nbsp;este organizarea pentru prima dată &icirc;n Rom&acirc;nia a&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp</a>&nbsp;la Timişoara &icirc;n 5-6 iunie 2010. Evenimentul, organizat &icirc;n parteneriat cu&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Universitatea Politehnica din Timişoara</a>, va reuni sute utilizatori şi dezvoltatori din Rom&acirc;nia, Ungaria, Ucraina, spațiul ex-iugoslav precum şi speakeri din comunitatea globală&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Despre Drupal</strong>. Este un pachet de software liber care permite unei persoane sau unei comunităţi de utilizatori de a publica cu uşurinţă, gestiona şi organiza un conţinut bogat pe un website. Sute de mii de oameni şi organizaţii&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">folosesc Drupal</a>&nbsp;pentru website-uri diferite ca putere, incluz&acirc;nd aici: portaluri web comunitare, site-uri de discuţii, site-uri &bdquo;corporate&rdquo;, aplicaţii intranet, site-uri personale sau blog-uri, aplicaţii e-Commerce, directoare de resurse, site-uri social networking.<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;este un&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">software opensource</a>&nbsp;distribuit sub&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a>&nbsp;(GNU General Public License &quot;) şi este menţinut şi dezvoltat de o comunitate de zeci de mii de utilizatori şi dezvoltatori.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Despre Asociaţia Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</strong>. Este o organizaţie, persoană juridică rom&acirc;nă de drept privat, cu caracter non-profit dedicată dezvoltării proiectului opensource&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. Asociaţia susţine comunitatea Drupal din Rom&acirc;nia cu finanţare, infrastructură, organizarea de evenimente, promovare şi distribuţia Drupal.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Despre Drupalcamp</strong>. Este un eveniment născut din dorinţa de a &icirc;mpărtăşi şi de a &icirc;nvăţa despre&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;&icirc;ntr-un mediu deschis. Este un eveniment intens cu discuţii, demo-uri şi cu interacţiune din partea participanţilor, care sunt actorii principali ai evenimentului. Drupalcam-urile sunt de fapt &bdquo;unconferences&rdquo;, adică exact opusul unei conferinţe oficiale (de exemplu OSCON, DrupalCon, LinuxCon, etc.). Participanţii propun subiecte &icirc;naintea evenimentului iar agenda este modelată &icirc;n funcţie aceste propuneri. Scopul Drupalcamp este acela de a conecta comunitatea locală şi regională şi a permite schimbul de idei.</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:5079:\"<p>Comunitatea utilizatorilor, dezvoltatorilor şi pasionaţilor de <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> din România anunţă înfiinţarea <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţiei Drupal România</a>. Principalul scop al Asociaţiei este promovarea sistemului <a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource</a> <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> ca sistem deschis pentru realizarea de situri portaluri web.</p>\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal România</a> este persoană juridică română cu caracter non-profit şi apolitică. Membrii fondatori ai Asociaţiei sunt: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a> şi <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\n<p>Organizaţia nou înfiinţată în România îşi propune promovarea <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>; susţinerea Comunităţii Drupal din România prin furnizarea de suport şi documentaţie localizate în română; organizarea de evenimente (conferinţe, seminarii, întâlniri, prezentări, cursuri deschise, evenimente media). Se vor stabili contacte şi parteneriate cu companii, instituţii publice, alte ONG-uri în vederea promovării <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal România</a> este parte şi contribuie la eforturile comunităţii globale<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Primul eveniment de marcă al <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţiei Drupal România</a> este organizarea pentru prima dată în România a <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp</a> la Timişoara în 5-6 iunie 2010. Evenimentul, organizat în parteneriat cu <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Universitatea Politehnica din Timişoara</a>, va reuni sute utilizatori şi dezvoltatori din România, Ungaria, Ucraina, spațiul ex-iugoslav precum şi speakeri din comunitatea globală <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Despre Drupal</strong>. Este un pachet de software liber care permite unei persoane sau unei comunităţi de utilizatori de a publica cu uşurinţă, gestiona şi organiza un conţinut bogat pe un website. Sute de mii de oameni şi organizaţii <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">folosesc Drupal</a> pentru website-uri diferite ca putere, incluzând aici: portaluri web comunitare, site-uri de discuţii, site-uri „corporate”, aplicaţii intranet, site-uri personale sau blog-uri, aplicaţii e-Commerce, directoare de resurse, site-uri social networking.<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> este un <a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">software opensource</a> distribuit sub <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a> (GNU General Public License \") şi este menţinut şi dezvoltat de o comunitate de zeci de mii de utilizatori şi dezvoltatori.</p>\n<p><strong>Despre Asociaţia Drupal România</strong>. Este o organizaţie, persoană juridică română de drept privat, cu caracter non-profit dedicată dezvoltării proiectului opensource <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. Asociaţia susţine comunitatea Drupal din România cu finanţare, infrastructură, organizarea de evenimente, promovare şi distribuţia Drupal.</p>\n<p><strong>Despre Drupalcamp</strong>. Este un eveniment născut din dorinţa de a împărtăşi şi de a învăţa despre <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> într-un mediu deschis. Este un eveniment intens cu discuţii, demo-uri şi cu interacţiune din partea participanţilor, care sunt actorii principali ai evenimentului. Drupalcam-urile sunt de fapt „unconferences”, adică exact opusul unei conferinţe oficiale (de exemplu OSCON, DrupalCon, LinuxCon, etc.). Participanţii propun subiecte înaintea evenimentului iar agenda este modelată în funcţie aceste propuneri. Scopul Drupalcamp este acela de a conecta comunitatea locală şi regională şi a permite schimbul de idei.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:10:\"field_tags\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:3:\"tid\";s:2:\"14\";}}}s:16:\"field_main_image\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:13:{s:3:\"fid\";s:2:\"17\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"filename\";s:28:\"asociatia-drupal-romania.png\";s:3:\"uri\";s:37:\"public://asociatia-drupal-romania.png\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:4:\"6676\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1348558708\";s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:0:{}s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"197\";s:6:\"height\";s:2:\"65\";}}}s:12:\"field_images\";a:0:{}s:11:\"title_field\";a:2:{s:2:\"ro\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"value\";s:42:\"A luat fiinţă Asociaţia Drupal România\";s:6:\"format\";N;s:10:\"safe_value\";s:42:\"A luat fiinţă Asociaţia Drupal România\";}}s:2:\"en\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"value\";s:38:\"Drupal Romania Association was founded\";s:6:\"format\";N;s:10:\"safe_value\";s:38:\"Drupal Romania Association was founded\";}}}s:22:\"field_main_image_style\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:\"value\";s:10:\"left-image\";}}}s:14:\"title_original\";s:42:\"A luat fiinţă Asociaţia Drupal România\";s:12:\"translations\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"original\";s:2:\"ro\";s:4:\"data\";a:2:{s:2:\"ro\";a:9:{s:11:\