;s:1:\"0\";s:4:\"data\";s:301:\"a:10:{s:16:\"ckeditor_default\";s:1:\"t\";s:20:\"ckeditor_show_toggle\";s:1:\"t\";s:14:\"ckeditor_popup\";s:1:\"f\";s:13:\"ckeditor_skin\";s:4:\"kama\";s:15:\"ckeditor_expand\";s:1:\"t\";s:14:\"ckeditor_width\";s:4:\"100%\";s:13:\"ckeditor_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:18:\"ckeditor_auto_lang\";s:1:\"t\";s:7:\"contact\";i:1;s:7:\"overlay\";i:1;}\";}',0,1411302448,1),('15','O:8:\"stdClass\":32:{s:3:\"vid\";s:2:\"15\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"About us\";s:3:\"log\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"comment\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"promote\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"sticky\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"nid\";s:2:\"15\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"page\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"ro\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1348556544\";s:7:\"changed\";s:10:\"1348611437\";s:4:\"tnid\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"translate\";s:1:\"0\";s:18:\"revision_timestamp\";s:10:\"1348611437\";s:12:\"revision_uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"body\";a:2:{s:2:\"en\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:3656:\"<p><strong>Drupal Romania Association</strong>&nbsp;is a non-profit Romanian legal entity committed to support the development of the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;opensouce project. The Association supports the Drupal Romanian Community by providing funding, infrastructure, supporting event organization, promoting and distributing Drupal.</p>\r\n<p>The Association&rsquo;s founding members are&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The association aims to promote the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;as a opensource system for creating websites, by:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Promoting&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;as an open system for websites building through events, web or mass-media.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Attracting developers, translators, consultants to provide free services to the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;Community.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Organizing&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;events like: conferences, seminars, meetings, presentations, open trainings, media events, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Supporting the Romanian localization of user interface of&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>and contrib modules.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Providing free&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;support and documentations in Romanian language.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Supporting the building of the Romanian Community website.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		To contact and establish partnerships with various companies, public institutions and NGOs in order to promote&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;and opensource software.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;is a contributor as well as a participant to the global&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;Community.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Drupal</strong>. It&#39;s a free software package that allows a person or a community to easily publish, manage and organize rich online content. Hundreds of thousands of people and organizations&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">use Drupal</a>&nbsp;to implement various websites, including community portals, discussion groups, intranet applications, personal websites and blogs, e-Commerce applications, repositories and social networks.&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;is<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource software</a>&nbsp;distributed under&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a>&nbsp;(GNU General Public License) and it is maintained and developed by a large community of users and developers.</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:3490:\"<p><strong>Drupal Romania Association</strong> is a non-profit Romanian legal entity committed to support the development of the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> opensouce project. The Association supports the Drupal Romanian Community by providing funding, infrastructure, supporting event organization, promoting and distributing Drupal.</p>\n<p>The Association’s founding members are <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a> and <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\n<p>The association aims to promote the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> as a opensource system for creating websites, by:</p>\n<ul><li>\n		Promoting <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> as an open system for websites building through events, web or mass-media.</li>\n<li>\n		Attracting developers, translators, consultants to provide free services to the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> Community.</li>\n<li>\n		Organizing <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> events like: conferences, seminars, meetings, presentations, open trainings, media events, etc.</li>\n<li>\n		Supporting the Romanian localization of user interface of <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>and contrib modules.</li>\n<li>\n		Providing free <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> support and documentations in Romanian language.</li>\n<li>\n		Supporting the building of the Romanian Community website.</li>\n<li>\n		To contact and establish partnerships with various companies, public institutions and NGOs in order to promote <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> and opensource software.</li>\n</ul><p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> is a contributor as well as a participant to the global <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> Community.</p>\n<p><strong>About Drupal</strong>. It\'s a free software package that allows a person or a community to easily publish, manage and organize rich online content. Hundreds of thousands of people and organizations <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">use Drupal</a> to implement various websites, including community portals, discussion groups, intranet applications, personal websites and blogs, e-Commerce applications, repositories and social networks. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> is<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">opensource software</a> distributed under <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a> (GNU General Public License) and it is maintained and developed by a large community of users and developers.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"ro\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:4011:\"<p><strong>Asociaţia Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</strong>&nbsp;este o organizaţie, persoană juridică rom&acirc;nă de drept privat, cu caracter non-profit dedicată dezvoltării proiectului opensource&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. Asociaţia susţine comunitatea Drupal din Rom&acirc;nia cu finanţare, infrastructură, organizarea de evenimente, promovare şi distribuţia Drupal.</p>\r\n<p>Membrii fondatori ai Asociaţiei sunt:&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>,&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a>&nbsp;şi&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Organizaţia &icirc;şi propune promovarea sistemului &bdquo;opensource&rdquo;&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;pentru realizarea de situri web prin:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Promovarea&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;ca sistem deschis pentru realizarea de portaluri web prin evenimente, pe web sau prin mass-media.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Atragerea de programatori, traducători, consultanţi care să presteze servicii &icirc;n mod voluntar pentru comunitatea&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Organizarea de evenimente&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>: conferinţe, seminarii, &icirc;nt&acirc;lniri, prezentări, cursuri deschise, evenimente media, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Să sprijine, prin voluntariat, localizarea sistemului&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;&icirc;n limba rom&acirc;nă.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Să furnizeze, prin voluntariat, suport şi documentaţii&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>localizate &icirc;n limba rom&acirc;nă.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Să sprijine realizarea unui sit destinat comunităţii Drupal din Rom&acirc;nia.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Să stabilească contacte şi parteneriate cu companii, instituţii publice, alte ONG-uri pentru a promova&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;şi softul &bdquo;opensource&rdquo;, &icirc;n general.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal Rom&acirc;nia</a>&nbsp;este parte şi contribuie la eforturile comunităţii globale&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Despre Drupal</strong>. Este un pachet de software liber care permite unei persoane sau unei comunităţi de utilizatori de a publica cu uşurinţă, gestiona şi organiza un conţinut bogat pe un website. Sute de mii de oameni şi organizaţii&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">folosesc Drupal</a>&nbsp;pentru website-uri diferite ca putere, incluz&acirc;nd aici: portaluri web comunitare, site-uri de discuţii, site-uri &bdquo;corporate&rdquo;, aplicaţii intranet, site-uri personale sau blog-uri, aplicaţii e-Commerce, directoare de resurse, site-uri social networking. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>&nbsp;este un&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">software opensource</a>&nbsp;distribuit sub&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a>&nbsp;(GNU General Public License) şi este menţinut şi dezvoltat de o comunitate de zeci de mii de utilizatori şi dezvoltatori.</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:3770:\"<p><strong>Asociaţia Drupal România</strong> este o organizaţie, persoană juridică română de drept privat, cu caracter non-profit dedicată dezvoltării proiectului opensource <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>. Asociaţia susţine comunitatea Drupal din România cu finanţare, infrastructură, organizarea de evenimente, promovare şi distribuţia Drupal.</p>\n<p>Membrii fondatori ai Asociaţiei sunt: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/313647\">Diana Precup</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/8662\">Alexandru Badiu</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/56348\">Claudiu Cristea</a>, <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/154006\">Gabriel Dragomir</a> şi <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\" href=\"http://drupal.org/user/279352\">Gabriel Ungureanu</a>.</p>\n<p>Organizaţia îşi propune promovarea sistemului „opensource” <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> pentru realizarea de situri web prin:</p>\n<ul><li>\n		Promovarea <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> ca sistem deschis pentru realizarea de portaluri web prin evenimente, pe web sau prin mass-media.</li>\n<li>\n		Atragerea de programatori, traducători, consultanţi care să presteze servicii în mod voluntar pentru comunitatea <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</li>\n<li>\n		Organizarea de evenimente <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>: conferinţe, seminarii, întâlniri, prezentări, cursuri deschise, evenimente media, etc.</li>\n<li>\n		Să sprijine, prin voluntariat, localizarea sistemului <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> în limba română.</li>\n<li>\n		Să furnizeze, prin voluntariat, suport şi documentaţii <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>localizate în limba română.</li>\n<li>\n		Să sprijine realizarea unui sit destinat comunităţii Drupal din România.</li>\n<li>\n		Să stabilească contacte şi parteneriate cu companii, instituţii publice, alte ONG-uri pentru a promova <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> şi softul „opensource”, în general.</li>\n</ul><p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţia Drupal România</a> este parte şi contribuie la eforturile comunităţii globale <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Despre Drupal</strong>. Este un pachet de software liber care permite unei persoane sau unei comunităţi de utilizatori de a publica cu uşurinţă, gestiona şi organiza un conţinut bogat pe un website. Sute de mii de oameni şi organizaţii <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org/cases\" href=\"http://drupal.org/cases\">folosesc Drupal</a> pentru website-uri diferite ca putere, incluzând aici: portaluri web comunitare, site-uri de discuţii, site-uri „corporate”, aplicaţii intranet, site-uri personale sau blog-uri, aplicaţii e-Commerce, directoare de resurse, site-uri social networking. <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a> este un <a fcksavedurl=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software\">software opensource</a> distribuit sub <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\" href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a> (GNU General Public License) şi este menţinut şi dezvoltat de o comunitate de zeci de mii de utilizatori şi dezvoltatori.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:11:\"title_field\";a:2:{s:2:\"en\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"value\";s:8:\"About us\";s:6:\"format\";N;s:10:\"safe_value\";s:8:\"About us\";}}s:2:\"ro\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"value\";s:10:\"Despre noi\";s:6:\"format\";N;s:10:\"safe_value\";s:10:\"Despre noi\";}}}s:17:\"field_attachments\";a:0:{}s:14:\"title_original\";s:10:\"Despre noi\";s:12:\"translations\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"original\";s:2:\"ro\";s:4:\"data\";a:2:{s:2:\"ro\";a:9:{s:11:\"entity_type\";s:4:\"node\";s:9:\"entity_id\";s:2:\"15\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"ro\";s:6:\"source\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"translate\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1348556544\";s:7:\"changed\";s:10:\"1348556544\";}s:2:\"en\";a:9:{s:11:\"entity_type\";s:4:\"node\";s:9:\"entity_id\";s:2:\"15\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"en\";s:6:\"source\";s:2:\"ro\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"translate\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"created\";s:10:\"1348556655\";s:7:\"changed\";s:10:\"1348556663\";}}}s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:9:{s:7:\"rdftype\";a:1:{i:0;s:13:\"foaf:Document\";}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:1:{i:0;s:8:\"dc:title\";}}s:7:\"created\";a:3:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:2:{i:0;s:7:\"dc:date\";i:1;s:10:\"dc:created\";}s:8:\"datatype\";s:12:\"xsd:dateTime\";s:8:\"callback\";s:12:\"date_iso8601\";}s:7:\"changed\";a:3:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"dc:modified\";}s:8:\"datatype\";s:12:\"xsd:dateTime\";s:8:\"callback\";s:12:\"date_iso8601\";}s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:1:{i:0;s:15:\"content:encoded\";}}s:3:\"uid\";a:2:{s:10:\"predicates\";a:1:{i:0;s:16: