mmary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:1199:\"<p>Primul eveniment de marcă al <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Asociaţiei Drupal România</a> este organizarea pentru prima dată în România a <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Drupalcamp</a> la Timişoara în 5-6 iunie 2010. Evenimentul, organizat în parteneriat cu<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Universitatea Politehnica din Timişoara</a>, va reuni sute utilizatori şi dezvoltatori din România, Ungaria, Ucraina, spațiul ex-iugoslav precum şi speakeri din comunitatea globală <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org\" href=\"http://drupal.org/\">Drupal</a>.</p>\n<p>Pe lângă <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Universitatea Politehnica din Timişoara</a>suntem susținuți ca și parteneri de către: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://ligaac.ro/\" href=\"http://ligaac.ro/\">Liga Studenţilor de la Facultatea de Automatică şi Calculatoare</a> și <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\" href=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\">Incubatorul de Afaceri Software</a>. O serie de alte organizaţii şi companii şi-au anunţat deja susţinerea pentru acest eveniment.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}s:2:\"en\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:1256:\"<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a>&nbsp;currently organizes its first major event, the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Timisoara 2010 Drupalcamp</a>, taking place during 5th and 6th of June, 2010. The event is organized in partnership with the&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technical University of Timisoara</a>&nbsp;and will host hundreds of users and developers from Romania, Hungary, Ucraine, Serbia, Bosnia, Croatia and other Central and East European states, as well as speakers from the global Drupal Community.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technic University of Timisoara</a>are supported as partners by:&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://ligaac.ro/\" href=\"http://ligaac.ro/\">League of Students from the Faculty of Automatics and Computers</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\" href=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\">Software Business Incubator</a>. A number of other organizations and companies have already announced their support for this event. We will return with details after completion of collaboration agreements.</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:1222:\"<p><a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupal.org.ro\" href=\"http://drupal.org.ro/\">Drupal Romania Association</a> currently organizes its first major event, the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://drupalcamp.ro\" href=\"http://drupalcamp.ro/\">Timisoara 2010 Drupalcamp</a>, taking place during 5th and 6th of June, 2010. The event is organized in partnership with the <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technical University of Timisoara</a> and will host hundreds of users and developers from Romania, Hungary, Ucraine, Serbia, Bosnia, Croatia and other Central and East European states, as well as speakers from the global Drupal Community.</p>\n<p>In addition to <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.upt.ro/\" href=\"http://www.upt.ro/\">Technic University of Timisoara</a>are supported as partners by: <a fcksavedurl=\"http://ligaac.ro/\" href=\"http://ligaac.ro/\">League of Students from the Faculty of Automatics and Computers</a> and <a fcksavedurl=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\" href=\"http://www.it-incubator.biz/\">Software Business Incubator</a>. A number of other organizations and companies have already announced their support for this event. We will return with details after completion of collaboration agreements.</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\"